@startuml sequence_results_page
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Search Results Page — Render Flow

actor Visitor
participant "Razor Pages\nRouter" as Router
participant "SearchIndexModel" as Model
participant "SearchArticlesQuery\nHandler" as Handler
participant "ArticleRepository" as Repo
database "SQL Server FTS" as DB
participant "Index.cshtml" as View

Visitor -> Router: GET /search?q=clean+architecture&page=1
Router -> Model: OnGetAsync("clean+architecture", 1)
Model -> Model: HTML-encode query for display
Model -> Model: Validate: length 2–200 chars
Model -> Handler: Send(SearchArticlesQuery)
Handler -> Repo: SearchAsync("clean+architecture", 1, 10)
Repo -> DB: CONTAINSTABLE ranked query
DB --> Repo: Ranked rows + total count = 42
Repo --> Handler: (List<SearchResultDto>, 42)
Handler --> Model: PagedResponse (Page=1, Total=42, TotalPages=5)
Model -> Model: IsEmpty = false
Model -> View: Model binding
View -> View: Render 10 result <article> cards\nwith <mark> highlights, dates, thumbnails
View -> View: Render pagination (5 pages, page 1 active)
View -> View: Set <title>clean+architecture — Search | Blog</title>
View -> View: Set Cache-Control: no-store
View --> Visitor: 200 OK HTML

@enduml
